Mattel Aquarius !!
Tested under the "Virtual Aquarius" emulator, by James the Animal Tamer.

The "bin2caq" tool creates two files: a basic loader and a pseudo array file.
To compile and run

- compile the program:				zcc +aquarius program.c
- convert it:					bin2caq a.bin program.caq
- run the emulator				aquarius
- from within the emulator, load the loader:	cload
- press ENTER twice, then play the "_program.caq" cassette file (loader)
- at the "OK" prompt, type RUN <ENTER>
- press ENTER twice, then play the "program.caq" cassette file
- wait... then have fun !



